text.tspan: This is a very simple mod that opens the door to very complex things.
URL Post Wand reports target block or entity data.
Any user may 'use', only obtained via /give command.
Using the URL Config Wand on Signs, Chests, Barrels,
Comparators, Sculk and Light Sensors, Lecterns,
and most Entites and Mobs... ...will enable/disable change reporting.
Any user may 'use', only obtained via /give command.
Chests, Hoppers, Dispensers, Droppers, and Barrels report contents when changed
Signs and Hanging Signs report front and back text
Sculk sensors transmit frequency, phase, and power level in real-time
Daylight sensors transmit power and invert status
Comparators report power level changes in real-time
Entities report user interactions (right-click) in real-time
"x": X coordinate of block or entity,
"y": Y coordinate of block or entity,
"z": Z coordinate of block or entity,
Most URLium devices transmit these fields in addition to device-specific data:
